title: Welcome to The Quest Journal
content:
This is your first tale in The Quest Journal! 

This journal is designed to chronicle your learning adventures with a medieval aesthetic. Each post is a "tale" in your ongoing quest for knowledge.

To begin writing:
1. Click the hidden admin symbol (âš”) in the footer
2. Enter your password
3. Optionally add your GitHub token for cross-device sync
4. Start penning your tales!

Your posts will be stored in this repository and visible to anyone who visits your GitHub Pages site. This makes it perfect for sharing your learning journey with potential employers.

Feel free to delete this welcome post once you're ready to start your own chronicle!
